    <note>Wang(2) Kai(2) [7379] Shen(1)'s [7376] and Dang's [1889] grandfather, betrothed to Zhang(1) Tian's [7166] younger sister, related to Wang(2) Tao [1883]. His ancestors were originally Taiyuan people, but when his grandfather died, the family moved to Jingzhao. The family (jia) was wealthy. Since his great grandfather and grandfather died in the military service, he was appointed to a military post. He distinguished himself as a general in the Tangut (XiXia) wars against Zhao Yuanhao. DDSL, 20.7a. CBD, 1, 182-3.</note>
